---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
const lastUpdated = 'March 16, 2025';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | ConstructionCalc"
  description="Privacy policy for ConstructionCalc.com — how we handle your data and what information we collect."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-6 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">1. Who we are</h2>
        <p>ConstructionCalc (<strong>constructioncalculate.com</strong>) is a free online calculator tool operated by Francisco Ruiz Lozano, based in Spain. Contact: <a href="mailto:franruizlozano31@gmail.com" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">franruizlozano31@gmail.com</a></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">2. Data we collect</h2>
        <p>ConstructionCalc does not collect, store, or process any personal data from users.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>All calculations are performed locally in your browser. No input data is sent to our servers.</li>
          <li>We do not use contact forms, user accounts, or registration systems.</li>
          <li>We do not use advertising networks or third-party tracking pixels.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">3. Google Search Console</h2>
        <p>We use Google Search Console for webmaster verification and to monitor site performance in Google Search. This tool does not collect personal data from visitors and does not place cookies on your device. Google may process anonymised technical data related to search indexing as part of their standard services. For more information, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">4. Cookies</h2>
        <p>ConstructionCalc does not use cookies for tracking, analytics, or advertising purposes. Your browser may store basic session data as part of normal web browsing, but we do not read or use this data.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">5. Third-party services</h2>
        <p>Our site is hosted on GitHub Pages (operated by GitHub, Inc., a subsidiary of Microsoft). GitHub may collect standard server logs (IP address, browser type, page visited, timestamp) as part of their infrastructure. This data is processed by GitHub under their own <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">6. Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
        <p>As a user located in the European Economic Area, you have rights under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), including the right to access, rectify, erase, or object to the processing of your personal data. Since we do not collect personal data, these rights do not practically apply. However, if you have any concern, you may contact us at <a href="mailto:franruizlozano31@gmail.com" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">franruizlozano31@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">7. Children's privacy</h2>
        <p>ConstructionCalc is not directed at children under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect data from minors.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">8. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">9. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at: <a href="mailto:franruizlozano31@gmail.com" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline">franruizlozano31@gmail.com</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
      <a href={`${base}/`} class="text-brand-600 hover:underline text-sm">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
